Class Description
Analysis

Constructs and returns an Analysis object.

AvgGovtExpEdu

Implements the interface defined by Analysis.
ComputationServer

Data
This class defines the object returned by the Reader when it reads data from the World Bank Database.
HealthExpVsMort
Analysis algorithm for health expenditure vs mortality rate Implements analysis interface
LineChart
Class for creating the line chart viewer used for presenting data.
LoginSessionManager
This class is in charge of displaying the Login Panel, collecting the User's credentials, and launching the MainUI.
MainUI
This class consists of the MainUI that the User uses to select aspects of desired analysis and displays corresponding Viewers once aspects are selected.
PieChart
Class that is used to create and display a pie chart graph.
PM2VsForest
Class that is used to create the result for the analysis of average forest size versus air quality
RCO2AndGDP
Implements the interface defined by Analysis.
Reader
Responsible for data acquisition from the World Bank's data base.
Report
Class that is used to create and display a report.
Result
Consists of all the data that has been processed and needed for rendering viewers.
RGovtExpEduVsHealthExp

RHspBedsAndHealthExp
Implements the interface defined by Analysis.
ScatterChart
Implements the interface defined by Viewer.
Selection
Contains all aspects of analysis selected by the User.
TimeSeries
Implements the interface defined by Viewer.
VerificationServer
Contains all valid credentials.
Viewer
Specifies the interface of the objects that can be manufactured by ViewerFactory.
ViewerFactory
Constructs and returns a Viewer.
ViewTheWorld
This is the main class of the system.
